title: GROVE PARK WESTSIDE PARK! FULLY RENOVATED!  HARDWOODS!
posting_body: ['FULLY RENOVATED!', 'HARDWOODS!', 'NEW APPLIANCES!', 'We DO NOT take section 8.', 'Great house in Grove Park.', ' Lots of windows, skylight, great sunlight, formal dinning room, huge kitchen, decorative fireplace, fenced dog run, large tranquil yard bordered by Proctor creek, extremely quiet and safe dead-end street.', '3 bedrooms 2 bath, central heat and air, laundry room, basement storage.', ' We DO NOT take section 8.', 'Adjacent to the Westside Park and the Proctor Creek Greenway.', ' Walking distance to schools, Kipp school, Marta and Grove park with a playground, tennis courts and a recreation center.', 'Great friendly neighborhood.', 'Less than 10 minutes from downtown, universities and shopping You will enjoy coming home!', '$2150 per month and $2200 security.', 'Available for an August 1 move in.', 'Pets are welcome with a $250 pet deposit.', 'We verify income and rental history.', 'Utilities are not included.', 'These are the only pictures available.', 'We DO NOT take section 8.', '"Still Available" messages will not be replied to.', 'Do not contact to ask if we are selling this property!!!', '24 Grove Park PL Atlanta 30318.', 'Please text me to arrange a viewing.', 'FOUR ZERO FOUR 434- 8649', 'Thanks for looking!']
